lfsom.data

Class LFSData

  • java.lang.Object
    • lfsom.data.LFSData

  • public class LFSData
extends java.lang.Object
    Reads data from a csv. Rows are separated by newlines, and columns by commas. First line contains attribute names.
    Version:
